<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/31/21402897/8bitdo-wireless-arcade-stick-nintendo-switch-pc-price">8BitDo 为 Switch 和 PC 推出无线街机摇杆</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362399" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3_Details.0.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3_Details.0.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3_Details.0-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3_Details.0-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3_Details.0-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，8BitDo 推出了一款对 Mod 友好的无线摇杆控制器，适用于 PC 和 Switch，续航时间约为 40 小时，定价 89.99 美元（约人民币 621 元），现已接受预定。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362400" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5_Dynamic_Button_Layout__1_.gif" alt="" width="800" height="593" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5_Dynamic_Button_Layout__1_.gif 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5_Dynamic_Button_Layout__1_-360x267.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5_Dynamic_Button_Layout__1_-768x569.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>值得指出的是，当用户在 PC 和 Switch 间切换时，按钮旁的标注将发生改变，以创造更直观的区分。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/506/461.htm">iPhone 12 部分机型或配备 LiDAR 激光传感器</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362395" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-Pro-camera-iPhone-12-camera.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="938" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-Pro-camera-iPhone-12-camera.jpg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-Pro-camera-iPhone-12-camera-360x225.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-Pro-camera-iPhone-12-camera-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-Pro-camera-iPhone-12-camera-1024x640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>
<p>IT 之家援引 DigiTimes 一份新报告指出，苹果将把 LiDAR「融入到一些新的 iPhone 机型中」，并说明苹果不会在所有新机型上采用该配置，因此应该是在 Pro 机型会配备。</p>
<p>LiDAR 是「光检测和测距」的缩写，首次搭载该技术的苹果产品是 2020 年的 iPad Pro，能显着改善增强现实体验，此前该技术主要用于汽车行业。</p>
<p>据此前爆料，LiDAR 只会出现在 6.7 英寸的 iPhone 12 Pro Max 上，但也有消息称，该功能将出现在 6.1 英寸和 6.7 英寸的 iPhone 12 Pro 机型上。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1022903.htm">联想发布 Tab P11 Pro 平板电脑</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362401" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/7ef73a29712b621.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="394" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/7ef73a29712b621.jpg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/7ef73a29712b621-360x203.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，联想发布了平板电脑 Tab P11 Pro，搭载了高通骁龙 730G 芯片组，采用了 11.5 英寸 2560&#215;1600 的 OLED 显示屏，四面的边框厚度为 6.9mm，支持 HDR10 和杜比视界 HDR。此外，它还拥有 4 个 2.5cc 腔体的 JBL 扬声器，经过杜比 Atmos 优化。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2020/08/31/app-store-bug-fixes-guideline-challenges/?scrolla=5eb6d68b7fedc32c19ef33b4">苹果确认两个 App Store 重要改变生效</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362402" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/app-store-on-ios-13.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/app-store-on-ios-13.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/app-store-on-ios-13-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/app-store-on-ios-13-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>MacRumors 消息，在今年的 WWDC 上，苹果宣布 App Store 审核将迎来两个改变：</p>
<p>第一，已上架应用为修复漏洞更新的版本如果触犯 App Store 规则，苹果不会阻止其上线，允许开发者在下一次递交版本中解决问题；第二，应用被判断违反 App Store 规则时，开发者除了可对判定进行上诉外，还能对规则本身的合理性提出质疑。</p>
<p>苹果宣布这两个改变现在已经正式生效。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2020-08-31/doc-iivhvpwy4106911.shtml">中国银联发布首款数字银行卡「银联无界卡」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362403" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/231240odyjyyxbyjpdmxxs.jpg" alt="" width="1020" height="862" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/231240odyjyyxbyjpdmxxs.jpg 1020w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/231240odyjyyxbyjpdmxxs-360x304.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/231240odyjyyxbyjpdmxxs-768x649.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px" /></p>
<p>《证券时报》消息，中国银联联合合作伙伴发布首款数字银行卡「银联无界卡」，通过数字化服务满足消费、存取现、转账、手机闪付、条码支付等支付需求。</p>
<p>中国人民银行支付结算司一级巡视员樊爽文表示，银联无界卡实现了发卡模式、管理模式、安全应用全流程的数字化，是银行卡产业迈向数字化新阶段的重要一步。</p>
